HHP-8 型電力機車 (「大馬力八千」，High Horse Power 8000）是由[[龐巴迪運輸|龐巴迪運輸]]（Bombardier Transportation）與[[阿爾斯通|阿爾斯通公司]]（Alstom）合作製造的雙駕駛室電力機車，供[[美鐵|美鐵]]與[[馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路|馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路]]使用。本型車的電力牽引系統直接衍生於阿爾斯通公司为[[法国国家铁路|法国国家铁路]]製造的[[BB_36000型电力机车|BB 36000型电力机车]]。
由於數量太少加上可靠性較差，造成單位維護成本過高，使得美鐵尋求取代本型15輛機車以及較老舊的 EMD [[AEM-7型電力機車|AEM-7型電力機車]]的替代車。
[[File:MARC_Locomotive_4912.jpg|缩略图]]的 HHP-8 型電力機車於[[巴爾的摩|巴爾的摩]]賓州車站]]

==歷史與設計==

最初的15部HHP-8型電力機車的訂單，是美鐵在購進[[Acela特快|Acela特快]]時一起訂購的，雖然外型類似Acela特快，但這批車是真正的電力機車，為牽引客車所設計。<ref name="b1">{{citation|url = http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=9odNXTGhwyAC|title = Rails under the mighty Hudson: the story of the Hudson Tubes, the Pennsy tunnels, and Manhattan Transfer|author = Brian J. Cudahy|publisher = Fordham Univ Press|year = 2002|issn = 1534-1399|pages = 89–90|accessdate = 2014-03-19|archive-date = 2014-03-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320013052/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=9odNXTGhwyAC|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{citation| url = http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=f1i0GoqE3lUC| title = Public transportation: on the move...| author = Marc Wortman| author2 = Roger Yee| publisher = Visual Reference Publications| year = 2005| pages = 102| accessdate = 2014-03-19| archive-date = 2014-03-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140320013206/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=f1i0GoqE3lUC| dead-url = no}}</ref> 這批機車將用來取代美鐵的GE E60型與補充AEM-7型電力機車。<ref name="b1"/>

[[馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路|馬里蘭區域通勤鐵路]]也購入了6輛 HHP-8型電力機車，<ref name="d2"/> 行駛於賓州線的裴瑞維爾（Perryville）至華盛頓之間。

本型車車體由不鏽鋼製造，結構能吸收六百萬焦耳的撞擊力。<ref name="t1">{{citation|url = http://www.sonic.net/~mly/Caltrain-Electrification/2000-08-Rolling-Stock-Draft/a5.pdf|title = APPENDIX 5 : Design Data : High  Horsepower Electric Locomotive (for  Amtrak, MARC)|work = www.sonic.net|publisher = Bombardier Transportation|accessdate = 2014-03-19|archive-date = 2012-10-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121001051749/http://www.sonic.net/~mly/Caltrain-Electrification/2000-08-Rolling-Stock-Draft/a5.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref> 電力牽引系統直接使用阿爾斯通公司用於SNCF Class BB 36000型車的系統。設計最高時速可達{{convert|217|km/h|mph|abbr=on}} ，但營運最高時速限制在 {{convert|201|km/h|mph|abbr=on}}。<ref name="t1"/><ref name="d2">{{citation|url = http://sonic.net/~mly/Caltrain-Electrification/2000-08-Rolling-Stock-Draft/4.pdf|work = sonic.net|at = Section 4: ELECTRIC ROLLING STOCK EQUIPMENT POWER, 4.3.1.4 High Horsepower Amtrak/MARC Locomotive|date = August 2000|title = Caltrain Electrification Project|accessdate = 2014-03-19|archive-date = 2014-03-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309051459/http://sonic.net/~mly/Caltrain-Electrification/2000-08-Rolling-Stock-Draft/4.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref>

迄2011年止，美鐵在波士頓到華盛頓的東北走廊上有15輛HHP-8型電力機車行駛。<ref name="b2">{{citation| url = http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=U9u4Yrn0F54C| title = All Aboard: The Complete North American Train Travel Guide| author = Jim Loomis| publisher = Chicago Review Press| year = 2011| pages = 140| accessdate = 2014-03-19| archive-date = 2014-02-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223004824/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=U9u4Yrn0F54C| dead-url = no}}</ref> 

